[p][/p][h1][b]Thrive Where Others Burn[/b][/h1][p][/p][p align="center"]Stellaris: Season 09 completes on November 25th with the [b]Infernals Species Pack[/b] and the 4.2 ‘Corvus’ update.
[/p][previewyoutube="3-0mawoAFCg;full"][/previewyoutube][p][/p][p align="center"]Brought to you by Forgotten Empires in close collaboration with Paradox Development Studios, our most ambitious Species Pack so far examines extremophile life bathing in the heat of fiery volcanic worlds.[/p][p]
[img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/4ac458ec6f9db550a9c8e728c4a2df39f01f7e85.png"][/img][/p][p align="center"][i]The United Volcanoes of Earth[/i][/p][p]
[/p][h1][b]Turn up the Heat[/b][/h1][p align="center"][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/4f5374c4ba2acb31c46c5e4c7104a037df3fbfe2.png"][/img]
[/p][p align="center"]In the [b]Cosmic Dawn [/b]origin, your species roamed the stars in the early days of the galaxy. [/p][p align="center"]Trapped as the planets cooled, recent volcanic activity freed some of your people. Now it is time to look for other survivors across the stars.
[/p][p align="center"]The very star that brought life to your planet has become a threat in the [b]Red Giant[/b] origin. [/p][p align="center"]As it expands and overheats the system, your empire can embrace this change or gain strength through adversity.[/p][p]
[img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/83a5d072d54025dd3d07c84a1f7be219899b53f8.png"][/img][/p][p align="center"][/p][h1][b]Set the Universe on Fire[/b][/h1][p][/p][p align="center"][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/47efe98d1c40bb3feebd5ad2f8b12c6712e0e01c.png"][/img][/p][p align="center"][i]You’re my guiding light[/i][/p][p]
[/p][p align="center"]The Infernals Species Pack adds the Galactic Hyperthermia crisis path, terraforming on a [i]grander[/i] scale.[/p][p][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/b4f74df6badc2368a1d131918454063259343c81.png"][/img]
The universe began in fire, but has cooled down into a dark and hostile place. It’s time to fix that.[/p][h2]
[img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/53db8b94fa62a5a2c84bd2d0a5b141080505538e.png"][/img][b]The Infernals Species Pack includes:[/b][/h2][list][*][p]Two new Origins:[/p][list][*][p]Cosmic Dawn[/p][/*][*][p]Red Giant[/p][/*][/list][/*][*][p]Galactic Hyperthermia Crisis Path[/p][/*][*][p]Four new Civics:[/p][list][*][p]Fire Cult[/p][/*][*][p]Scorched World Heralds / Pyromanic Instinct[/p][/*][*][p]Galvanic Empire / Biometallic Cartel / Galvanic Synthesis[/p][/*][*][p]Planet Forgers / Planetary Architects / Volcanic Nesting / Thermal Optimizers[/p][/*][/list][/*][*][p]Volcanic Planets and Habitability Preference[/p][/*][*][p]Thermophile Mechanics[/p][/*][*][p]Infernal Species Traits[/p][/*][*][p]10 Infernal Species Portraits[/p][/*][*][p]Infernal Shipset[/p][/*][*][p]Infernal Diplomatic Room, City Set, Advisor, Flag Emblems, and more.[/p][/*][/list][p align="center"][b]Dev Diary Schedule[/b][/p][table equalcells="1" colwidth=","][tr][td][p align="center"]October 30[/p][/td][td][p align="center"]Infernal Pops, Traits, and Volcanic Worlds[/p][/td][/tr][tr][td][p align="center"]November 6[/p][/td][td][p align="center"]Cosmic Dawn, Civics, Infernal Shipset[/p][/td][/tr][tr][td][p align="center"]November 13[/p][/td][td][p align="center"]Red Giant, Galactic Hyperthermia[/p][/td][/tr][tr][td][p align="center"]November 20[/p][/td][td][p align="center"]Infernals and 4.2.0 'Corvus' Preliminary Release Notes[/p][/td][/tr][/table][p]

[img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/171dde3009b1363627da8ef6e9e939475f78baad.jpg"][/img][/p][p align="center"][i]The Infernals Species Pack is included as part of [u][url="https://pdxint.at/47UvFwi"]Stellaris: Season 09[/url][/u][/i][/p][p][/p]